content: written crochet pdf pattern in english us terminology no charts or photos the crochet skill level is intermediate the pattern consists of 24 rounds for this project you need cotton thread 50 g / 1 76 oz / 308 yards / 282 m per skein 2 mm hook yardage 210 yards / 192 m finished size 11 / 28 cm if you have any questions feel free to contact me
